This paper deals with issues related to privacy and data protection, which are central to the field of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the analysis of large datasets and the use of statistical methods to draw conclusions, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also touches upon issues related to user behavior and user interfaces, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM).
